description:
Solo from the ballet Sleeping Beauty and
I. Carmen-Suite
Choreography by Alberto Alonso, music by Georges Bizet  Rodion Shchedrin
Performed by Oxana Skorik, Ivan Oskorbin, Roman Belyakov, Alexandra Iosifidi, Maxim Zenin

II. Le Spectre de la rose
Choreography by Michel Fokine, music by Carl Maria von Weber
Performed by Camilla Mazzi and Philipp Stepin

III. Adagio from the ballet Spartacus
horeography by Yuri Grigrovich, music by Aram Khatchaturian
Performed by Anastasia Matvienko and Danila Korsuntsev

IV. Pas de deux from Act III of the ballet The Sleeping Beauty
Choreography by Marius Petipa, revised version by Konstantin Sergeyev, music by Pyotr Tchaikovsky
Performed by Maria Khoreva and Yevgeny Konovalov

V. Duet from the ballet Romeo and Juliet
Choreography by Leonid Lavrovsky, music by Sergei Prokofiev
Performed by Yekaterina Osmolkina and Maxim Zyuzin

VI. A flashback
Choreography by Ilya Zhivoi, music by Arvo Prt
Performed by Ekaterina Kondaurova and Roman Belyakov
Performed to recorded music

VII. Pas de deux from Act II of the ballet Giselle
Choreography by Marius Petipa, music by Adolphe Adam
Performed by Viktoria Tereshkina and Xander Parish

VIII. The Dying Swan
Choreography by Michel Fokine, music by Camille Saint-Sans
Performed by Kristina Shapran

IX. Pas daction from the ballet Le Corsaire
Choreography by Alexander Chekrygin, music by Riccardo Drigo
Performed by Maria Iliushkina, Timur Askerov, Kimin Kim

The Mariinsky Orchestra
Conductor: Arseny Shuplyakov
